  "format": "The 900th episode is an all-voicemail mailbag (spoiler revenge, red-flag favorites, underrated rom-coms, a casting game), then reviews of You, Me, and Tuscany, The Christophers, and Blue Heron, plus Sean's interview with Sophy Romvari.",
  "segments": [
